  "detailed_description": "<strong>Explore an all-too-familiar, yet unfamiliar, world alongside beings known as Mogwai.</strong><br><br><u>HEARTBEAT</u> is a <i>top-down RPG</i> where you traverse a land recovering from multiple strifes between humans and Mogwai. The unaware populace lives in a constant state of uncertainty and danger veiled by a tranquil facade. As a Conjurer, a human marked by Mogwai, it is your duty to maintain the peace and ensure balance between all who share the earth beneath your feet. Meet new friends and foes as you take on this strange and transcendent journey.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984560/extras/1bf8d7f08cfbd1f5723e8e3030e1fc5b.poster.avif?t=1545874354\" width=558 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984560/extras/1bf8d7f08cfbd1f5723e8e3030e1fc5b.webm?t=1545874354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984560/extras/02d3453cd434ce1d507ae128e215e737.poster.avif?t=1545874354\" width=558 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984560/extras/02d3453cd434ce1d507ae128e215e737.webm?t=1545874354\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984560/extras/02d3453cd434ce1d507ae128e215e737.mp4?t=1545874354\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/984560/extras/e00a427506368e16f4f0f0f735590633.poster.avif?t=1545874354\" width=558 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akama